# See https://help.github.com/articles/ignoring-files/ for more about ignoring files.

# dependencies
**/node_modules/
**/.pnp
**/.pnp.*
**/.yarn/*
!**/.yarn/patches
!**/.yarn/plugins
!**/.yarn/releases
!**/.yarn/versions
**/.pnpm-store/
**/.npm/

# testing
**/coverage/

# next.js / build outputs
**/.next/
**/out/
**/build/
**/dist/
**/.turbo/
**/.cache/

# prisma generated artifacts
**/generated/prisma/
**/.prisma/
**/prisma/generated/

# debug
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/.pnpm-debug.log*

# env files (can opt-in for committing if needed)
**/.env*
!**/.env.example

# secrets
**/secrets.h
*.pem

# vercel
**/.vercel

# typescript
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/next-env.d.ts

# misc
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
